OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland and Fair Isle will be
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain, turning
OL,7,Fdrier from the west later this
OL,8,Fafternoon. Rain across Orkney this
OL,9,Fmorning followed by a few showers this
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late brightness and a
OL,13,Ffew showers this evening.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FOrkney will see the odd shower
OL,16,Fat first otherwise dry and sunny.
OL,17,FCloudy start with showers across
OL,18,FShetland, turning dry and bright by
OL,19,Fafternoon. Windy across Orkney late
OL,20,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
