OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FShetland wet and windy on Saturday,
OL,7,FOrkney seeing rain in the morning.
OL,8,FSunny spells and occasional showers on
OL,9,FSunday and Monday. Breezy on Sunday.
